results.description: A rugged, expandable, and brilliantly accessible carry-on travel backpack. Features top, side, front and rear access via weatherproof UltraZips. Expands to 45L for gear-hauling and collapses to 35L for day use. Quick-access pockets and tuck-away shoulder straps and hip belt.

Versatile, durable, and beautifully designed. Offers a streamlined yet spacious design with various compartments and adjustable FlexFold dividers for organization. Equipped with a laptop pocket, external carry straps, and weatherproof construction.

Functional and stylish messenger bag ideal for work and commuting, with customizable organization through FlexFold dividers. Weatherproof exterior and dedicated capture clip points for photography gear. Features top and side access, and a dedicated laptop sleeve.
